sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Operator as KubeRay Operator<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    participant HeadPod as Ray Head Pod<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    participant Workers as Ray Worker Pods
    participant Submitter as Submitter Job Pod
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant RBACProxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant TokenReview as TokenReview API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant SAR as SubjectAccessReview API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,Workers: Flow 1: RayJob Execution via K8sJobMode
    User->>K8sAPI: POST RayJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (kubectl)
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Watch event: RayJob created
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster (pods, services)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>HeadPod: Ray Head Pod scheduled
    K8sAPI-->>Workers: Ray Worker Pods scheduled
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Kubernetes Job (submitter)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Submitter: Submitter Job Pod scheduled
    Submitter->>HeadPod: POST /api/jobs (submit Ray job)<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    HeadPod-->>Submitter: Job ID response
    Operator->>HeadPod: GET /api/jobs/{id} (poll status)<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    HeadPod-->>Operator: Job status (RUNNING/SUCCEEDED/FAILED)

    Note over User,SAR: Flow 2: Authenticated Dashboard Access via Gateway API (RHOAI)
    User->>Gateway: GET /ray/{ns}/{cluster}/<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: OIDC Token
    Gateway->>RBACProxy: Forward to head pod sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS (self-signed)<br/>Auth: OIDC Token forwarded
    RBACProxy->>TokenReview: Validate OIDC token<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    TokenReview-->>RBACProxy: Token valid (user identity)
    RBACProxy->>SAR: Check authorization<br/>verb=get, resource=services<br/>resourceName={cluster}-head-svc
    SAR-->>RBACProxy: Authorized
    RBACProxy->>HeadPod: GET /dashboard (localhost)<br/>8265/TCP HTTP (local)
    HeadPod-->>RBACProxy: Dashboard HTML
    RBACProxy-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>User: Dashboard rendered

    Note over User,Workers: Flow 3: RayService Zero-Downtime Upgrade
    User->>K8sAPI: Update RayService spec<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Watch event: RayService updated
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create pending RayCluster<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>HeadPod: Pending Ray Head Pod ready
    Operator->>HeadPod: POST /api/serve/config (deploy new config)<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    HeadPod-->>Operator: Serve config applied
    Operator->>HeadPod: GET /api/serve/deployments (health check)<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    HeadPod-->>Operator: All deployments HEALTHY
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Update serve-svc selector → pending cluster<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Delete old active RayCluster<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
